# Docker Manual

## 1) Clone Repository & change .env.prod

```
git clone https://git.fe.up.pt/alexandre.valle/dei-acolhimento.git
```

## 2) Docker build & up

```
cd dei-acolhimento/src

docker-compose up -d --build
```

## First time setup DB

```
docker-compose exec app php artisan migrate --force

docker-compose exec app php artisan db:seed
```

## 3) Change the password of user postgres in container postgres:14

```
docker exec postgres:14 psql -c "alter user postgres with password '01230123';" -U postgres
```
